sentiment_score_definition: x <= -0.35: Bearish; -0.35 < x <= -0.15: Somewhat-Bearish; -0.15 < x < 0.15: Neutral; 0.15 <= x < 0.35: Somewhat_Bullish; x >= 0.35: Bullish
relevance_score_definition: 0 < x <= 1, with a higher score indicating higher relevance.

feed.title: While institutions own 25% of 1RT Acquisition Corp. (NASDAQ:ONCH), retail investors are its largest shareholders with 48% ownership
feed.summary: Retail investors hold the largest stake in 1RT Acquisition Corp. (NASDAQ:ONCH) with 48% ownership, giving them significant influence over management decisions, while institutions own 25%. The top 18 shareholders collectively control 50% of the business, with 1RT Sponsor LLC being the single largest shareholder at 21%. The company currently lacks analyst coverage.
